Sitting next to the jar should be an open laptop with a website on screen that reads 'Civitai.com' in a clean, modern font. The laptop and jar should be positioned in a way that suggests they are being used together, with the jar serving as a way to collect tips for the person using the laptop. The overall effect should be one of friendly, approachable charm, as if the person is inviting viewers to support their work." Highest-Quality, 4k, intricate details, visually stunning, Masterpiece
